{"tid":1987760,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇法律JJ可以解答下我，點解掟磚頭落地下同拎刀斬人仲要爭啲斬死人都係判45個月？？","createTime":"2020-04-24T16:40:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T09:55:57.000Z","uid":167426,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5910b9c9c68b110767ecd335ffa1328052a091","tid":1987760,"uid":167426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"1.  有被告掟了一塊磚 判監3年9個月<br />\n<br />\n法官指被告於案中掟過一塊磚，並沒擲中警員，但其行為等於認同其他犯事者，與其他犯事者互相給予安慰及支持，故須負上集體罪行刑罰。不過，因他曾免費向人施教，故就此善行獲減刑。<br />\n<br />\n2. 連儂隧道斬人男子判囚45個月　法庭指判刑需具阻嚇性<br />\n<br />\n法官同時指出，案中3名傷者傷害嚴重，其中曾任職記者的受害人，肺部萎縮，要切除少量組織，胸和肩部都受傷，如果不是即時送院，可能會有生命危險，事後她亦患上嚴重創傷後壓力症。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48144a46308c3f0b0de45bd5a6f806884b0e3071","tid":1987760,"uid":167426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" cla